snippet.textDisplay:
I don’t understand why Barca Fans voice is so unnoticeable by the team presidency. We are very conscious that Valverde is a professional and a very good manager but he is not for FC Barcelona. As simple as that. Maybe in an another world class team he would be very successful but in Barca not. These are facts that we all are seeing. Barca has a great team and they should seize the opportunity and use Messi’s magic to write history for more couple of years, because time is ticking and his retirement is not far away. We need a manager with a competitive heart, not a manager that watches the game like he is a spectator without saying any word like my 80y grandpa, without offending anyone but that’s a reality I see in every match.

SO PLEASE LIKE THE COMMENT AND LET IT BE UNDERSTOOD AS A DISSATISFACTION FROM BARCA FANS. WE SHOULD BE LISTEN. AS WE SAY:

MES QUE EN CLUB...
